Cutlass Aeronautics Fabricators

is a company mostly devoted to long range vessels in the Atmospheric Persuasion, though it really depends...

(Note: Most designs WILL USE MechJeb. Others will be listed with what uses it.)

-------------------------------------------------------------------

CAF-F01

(The CAF-F01 started as an attempt to replicate the P51 Mustang, but quickly became it\'s own plane.)

The CAF-F01 is a Single engined Plane using the TurboProp from the Damned Aeronautics part. a nice, stable craft with a good fuel economy.

(Unfortunately, I forgot to grab a pic of it taking it off.)

Here we see the CAF-F01B (CAF-F01 with droptanks) with it\'s tanks dropped and coasting at 2/3rd power, at the halfway point.

sighting land on the return trip.

Closing in on the Space center.

Landed at the Space center. (It is not shown here, but the plane still has One fuel cell left, and a little still left in the half-way tank.)
